//, {"isPV":false,"name":"Fever Feels Horrible, but is Actually Awesome!","videoId":"cRZOUcpiOxY","cardList":[{"s":1680,"e":8310,"r":"","p":"","t":"Fever feels bad. So we take medication \nto suppress it – but is this a good idea?","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":8310,"e":15896,"r":"","p":"","t":"It turns out fever is one of the oldest defenses \n against disease. What exactly is it,  how does","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":15896,"e":21770,"r":"","p":"","t":"it make your immune defense stronger \nand should you take a pill to combat it?","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":22680,"e":24000,"r":"","p":"","t":"The Heat of Life","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":25120,"e":30080,"r":"","p":"","t":"On earth life is able to thrive between \nthe extremes of -10°C in deep cool  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":30080,"e":37960,"r":"","p":"","t":"pools and 120°C in thermal vents. Step outside \nthis range and die. Every animal or microbe  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":37960,"e":43600,"r":"","p":"","t":"has a temperature range that is ideal and one \nthat is stressful but survivable for a while.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":43600,"e":47720,"r":"","p":"","t":"Your ideal temperature is where your cells \nwork best, where their internal machinery  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":47720,"e":52480,"r":"","p":"","t":"is the most efficient and the animal as \na whole the best adapted to its niche.  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":52480,"e":58080,"r":"","p":"","t":"Humans are warm blooded animals and our bodies \nexpend a lot of energy to keep us around 37°C  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":58680,"e":66120,"r":"","p":"","t":"or 98.6 °F. Which seems wasteful, but this \nmay actually be a defensive adaptation – our  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":66120,"e":71000,"r":"","p":"","t":"temperature makes us almost entirely immune \nto one of the worst killers and parasites:  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":71000,"e":79080,"r":"","p":"","t":"Fungi. Most colder animals and their insides \nare infected by them - but you are just too hot!","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":79080,"e":85600,"r":"","p":"","t":"Which brings us to fever. For any microbe that \nwants to infect you, your body is a world they  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":85600,"e":91800,"r":"","p":"","t":"want to conquer. Fever is defensive climate change \npushing an invader outside its ideal temperature  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":91800,"e":98680,"r":"","p":"","t":"range and making the world horrible. It evolved \nat least 600 million years ago and is widespread:  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":98680,"e":102000,"r":"","p":"","t":"most animals increase their core \ntemperature when they are sick.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":102000,"e":105880,"r":"","p":"","t":"Fish swim into warmer waters, \nlizards bathe in the sun. Bees  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":105880,"e":110560,"r":"","p":"","t":"heat up the air inside their hive.\nBut you, warm blooded mammal,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":110560,"e":116792,"r":"","p":"","t":"you have way more drastic options. Let's\nmake you sick and see what happens.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":117440,"e":120000,"r":"","p":"","t":"When Your Blood Turns Into Lava","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":120880,"e":126240,"r":"","p":"","t":"You're invaded by bacteria and viruses at \nthe same time. The invasion is powerful and  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":126240,"e":132240,"r":"","p":"","t":"you need to slow it down as fast as possible. \nFever is part of your first line of defense,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":132240,"e":135680,"r":"","p":"","t":"triggered by a diverse group \nof chemicals called “pyrogens”,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":135680,"e":140920,"r":"","p":"","t":"“The creators of heat”. They float away from \nthe battlefield and pass right into your brain,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":140920,"e":145840,"r":"","p":"","t":"where specialized receptors pick them up \nand crank up your internal thermostat.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":145840,"e":151240,"r":"","p":"","t":"First you begin to shiver. Your skeletal muscles \ncontract really quickly, which generates a lot of  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":151240,"e":157040,"r":"","p":"","t":"heat in your core. At the same time usually the \nblood vessels near your surfaces contract and  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":157040,"e":163640,"r":"","p":"","t":"prevent heat from escaping through your skin. \nYour skin cools down while your insides burn.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":163640,"e":168960,"r":"","p":"","t":"Fever is a systemic, body wide response and \nis a serious energy investment for your body.  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":168960,"e":173000,"r":"","p":"","t":"You burn about 10% more calories to stay \nalive for every degree centigrade your  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":173000,"e":178320,"r":"","p":"","t":"body temperature rises. Fever is also \na strong order to lay down and rest,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":178320,"e":182720,"r":"","p":"","t":"to save energy and give your \nimmune system time to fight.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":182720,"e":188147,"r":"","p":"","t":"Back to the battlefield: When the bacteria entered \nyour body they tried to be stealthy. But now they  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":188147,"e":193120,"r":"","p":"","t":"have switched into high production mode. Their \ngoal is to multiply as fast as possible, which  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":193120,"e":198240,"r":"","p":"","t":"means they need a lot of resources and are highly \nstressed. Imagine running a marathon while eating  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":198240,"e":204680,"r":"","p":"","t":"a succulent chinese meal and giving birth. The \nlast thing bacteria need right now is more stress.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":204680,"e":209440,"r":"","p":"","t":"So your immune system tries to stress them out \nas much as possible by ordering inflammation,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":209440,"e":211280,"r":"","p":"","t":"which floods the battlefield with fluids,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":211280,"e":217040,"r":"","p":"","t":"attack proteins and soldiers. Pretty \nstressful! Fever is even more stress!","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":217040,"e":220600,"r":"","p":"","t":"For the bacteria a moment ago the \ntemperature range was pleasant,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":220600,"e":226360,"r":"","p":"","t":"now the world burns! Heat can cause their \norgans to break and membranes to rupture,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":226360,"e":233080,"r":"","p":"","t":"damage their DNA and diminish protein production. \nThey are seriously suffering from the heat.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":233080,"e":239960,"r":"","p":"","t":"Why doesn't this affect your cells? It does! \nAll of this is stressful for your cells too!  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":239960,"e":245240,"r":"","p":"","t":"Virtually every system and organ of your \nbody works worse during fever – except one:  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":245240,"e":250880,"r":"","p":"","t":"Your immune system. Neutrophils are recruited \nfaster, Macrophages and Dendritic Cells are  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":250880,"e":256640,"r":"","p":"","t":"better at devouring enemies, Killer Cells \nkill better and so on. And fever animates  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":256640,"e":261120,"r":"","p":"","t":"your immune cells to gobble up the critical \nresources your enemies need, like iron,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":261120,"e":266000,"r":"","p":"","t":"glucose and glutamine, turning the \nbattlefield into a food desert.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":266000,"e":268520,"r":"","p":"","t":"The viruses that infected millions of cells are  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":268520,"e":273560,"r":"","p":"","t":"doing even worse because they are also \nvery sensitive to heat. For example,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":273560,"e":277680,"r":"","p":"","t":"The rhinovirus that causes the common \ncold can only infect your respiratory  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":277680,"e":283760,"r":"","p":"","t":"tract because it is significantly colder than \nthe rest of your body, even without fever. ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":283760,"e":287760,"r":"","p":"","t":"The heat is also really bad for the millions \nof cells that are infected by viruses  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":287760,"e":294280,"r":"","p":"","t":"at this point. They are working super hard \nproducing viruses, which is pretty stressful.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":294280,"e":299800,"r":"","p":"","t":"As the heat becomes too much to bear, the \nsuper stressed cells panic. As their internal  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":299800,"e":304680,"r":"","p":"","t":"machinery is breaking and failing they quickly \nproduce billions of heat shock proteins,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":304680,"e":309120,"r":"","p":"","t":"or HSPs, that start repairs, keeping them alive.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":309120,"e":311560,"r":"","p":"","t":"But this is a trap.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":311560,"e":317640,"r":"","p":"","t":"Even your healthy cells produce HSPs to deal with \nthe heat – but if a cell makes too many of them,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":317640,"e":321960,"r":"","p":"","t":"this means it is more stressed than it \nshould be. And if it is too stressed,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":321960,"e":328160,"r":"","p":"","t":"something is wrong and it should be killed. So \nyour Natural Killer Cells and Killer T Cells are  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":328160,"e":333560,"r":"","p":"","t":"activated and attracted by HSPs and start \nkilling infected cells and all the viruses  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":333560,"e":340560,"r":"","p":"","t":"inside them. By trying to protect themselves, \ninfected cells are calling out to be destroyed.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":340560,"e":343320,"r":"","p":"","t":"But if fever is such an effective weapon,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":343320,"e":348880,"r":"","p":"","t":"why don’t your enemies adapt to it? How is it \nstill viable, in so many different animals,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":348880,"e":357000,"r":"","p":"","t":"after hundreds of millions of years? A wild reason \nis that fever actually might outsmart evolution.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":357000,"e":360960,"r":"","p":"","t":"If your enemies survive fever long \nenough, natural selection changes  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":360960,"e":366840,"r":"","p":"","t":"them. The individuals that are better suited to \ndeal with heat reproduce more. After a few days,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":366840,"e":371280,"r":"","p":"","t":"they have adapted. But this becomes \na handicap – because the next step is  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":371280,"e":377480,"r":"","p":"","t":"to infect new victims in new bodies, and \nnow healthy humans are too cold for them!","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":377480,"e":383320,"r":"","p":"","t":"Not impossible to infect, just harder. And \nthe heat resistant microbes now compete  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":383320,"e":387280,"r":"","p":"","t":"with their cousins that like it colder \nand have an advantage infecting healthy  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":387280,"e":393040,"r":"","p":"","t":"hosts. This creates an evolutionary \ndilemma without a perfect solution.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":393040,"e":399014,"r":"","p":"","t":"To circumvent this, serious pathogens like \nmeasles use hit and run tactics. The measles virus  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":399014,"e":402920,"r":"","p":"","t":"replicates ultra fast and is the most infectious \nright before your fever hits with full force.  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":402920,"e":409240,"r":"","p":"","t":"It's brutally beaten back once your full immune \nresponse shows up. But by then the damage is done.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":409240,"e":412360,"r":"","p":"","t":"Fever is an effective part of \nthe puzzle of your immune system,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":412360,"e":415600,"r":"","p":"","t":"helping to attack and stress your \nenemies from as many angles as  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":415600,"e":420771,"r":"","p":"","t":"possible. But if fever is so great, \nwhy do we stop it when we are sick?","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":421480,"e":424321,"r":"","p":"","t":"Should you Fight Fever with Medications","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":425200,"e":428880,"r":"","p":"","t":"We think it is normal to have magic \npills, but relatively harmless,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":428880,"e":434160,"r":"","p":"","t":"over the counter pain medication like Aspirin or \nIbuprofen only became cheap and widely available  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":434160,"e":439600,"r":"","p":"","t":"in the last century or so. Going to a pharmacy to \nget something for your headache is extremely new  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":439600,"e":445200,"r":"","p":"","t":"in human history. Pain feels bad, so we've \ngotten used to stopping it when we feel it.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":445267,"e":449520,"r":"","p":"","t":"If you are sick, you're supposed to feel a reasonable \namount of pain so you lie down and save energy.  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":450240,"e":455760,"r":"","p":"","t":"This is not a bug but a feature of your immune \nsystem. But pain and fever are closely connected  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":455760,"e":461760,"r":"","p":"","t":"and over the counter pain medication like \nIbuprofen and Paracetamol also work against fever.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":461760,"e":467520,"r":"","p":"","t":"Especially in children fever is often suppressed \nby worried parents or doctors – sometimes because  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":467520,"e":473017,"r":"","p":"","t":"they think fever itself is the disease or they \nare worried that it can do long term harm. ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":473017,"e":479440,"r":"","p":"","t":"In general it's fair to say that for temperatures \nbelow 40°C or 104 °F, fever is not dangerous  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":480000,"e":483520,"r":"","p":"","t":"and doesn’t need to be treated.\nOf course there are also patients  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":483520,"e":487880,"r":"","p":"","t":"that should not have fever – like pregnant \nwomen, seniors and seriously weakened  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":487880,"e":495320,"r":"","p":"","t":"patients. For them the extra stress may be \ndangerous. Fever over 40°C is dangerous to  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":495320,"e":499880,"r":"","p":"","t":"anybody because it's most likely caused \nby your internal heat monitor failing.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":499880,"e":503127,"r":"","p":"","t":"Things get more complicated\nin serious disease territory.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":503127,"e":506475,"r":"","p":"","t":"We also have evidence that for \nsome diseases like influenza","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":506475,"e":510676,"r":"","p":"","t":"or chickenpox antifever drugs \ndo not help you to heal faster.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":510676,"e":512360,"r":"","p":"","t":"But we are also running \n into ethics problems here","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":512360,"e":517799,"r":"","p":"","t":"that make clinical trials difficult. In one \nstudy doctors gave strong anti fever treatment to  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":517799,"e":522919,"r":"","p":"","t":"critical care patients – but had to stop \nafter mortality shot up. Overall we have  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":522919,"e":528280,"r":"","p":"","t":"strong indications that more people may survive \nserious infectious diseases better with a fever.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":528280,"e":531520,"r":"","p":"","t":"And there is very little clinical \nevidence that stopping fever leads","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":531520,"e":535200,"r":"","p":"","t":"to better health outcomes. But \nthere are important exceptions,","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":535200,"e":540600,"r":"","p":"","t":"like neurological injuries and stroke.\nWe definitely need a lot more research.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":540600,"e":546080,"r":"","p":"","t":"So should you fight fever? Well, speak to \nyour doctor and don’t listen to internet  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":546080,"e":551840,"r":"","p":"","t":"videos. But this decision is really about \npayoffs. If a fever is not dangerously  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":551840,"e":557040,"r":"","p":"","t":"high and you can bear it, you are supporting \nyour defenses and may even get healthy a bit  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":557040,"e":561200,"r":"","p":"","t":"faster. But if you feel really bad \nand are healthy in general, ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":561200,"e":565080,"r":"","p":"","t":"taking a pill against pain and fever \nwill make you feel better quicker,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":565080,"e":568550,"r":"","p":"","t":"at the cost of a slightly \nless effective immune defense.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":568550,"e":572600,"r":"","p":"","t":"However you decide, the next time \nyou are burning up and feeling bad,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":572600,"e":578122,"r":"","p":"","t":"you can rest easy in the knowledge that your \nenemies are having a much worse time than you. ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":580080,"e":584080,"r":"","p":"","t":"It’s thanks to doctors and researchers \nthat we have these insights – we’re just  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":584080,"e":588040,"r":"","p":"","t":"doing our part by bringing them to \nyou. If you are also aiming to make  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":588040,"e":591080,"r":"","p":"","t":"a positive difference in the \nworld, where should you start?","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":591080,"e":596600,"r":"","p":"","t":"Today’s sponsor, 80,000 Hours, can help you \nwith that decision. 80,000 Hours is a nonprofit  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":596600,"e":601440,"r":"","p":"","t":"career advice organization that wants to help \npeople find fulfilling careers that also do a  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":601440,"e":607200,"r":"","p":"","t":"lot of good in the world. And their advice is \nfree, without any hidden cost or fee later on.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":607200,"e":612080,"r":"","p":"","t":"Like us, they care a lot about making sure their \nwork is based on the best available evidence and  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":612080,"e":617080,"r":"","p":"","t":"consultation with experts. So they’ve spent the \nlast decade compiling and conducting research  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":617080,"e":621960,"r":"","p":"","t":"into topics like 'how much impact can one \nperson actually have' and 'what are the  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":621960,"e":625760,"r":"","p":"","t":"best ways to make a positive difference \non important global issues'. Turns out,  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":625760,"e":630680,"r":"","p":"","t":"following a well-known career path isn’t your only \noption to achieve that goal. In fact, there may  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":630680,"e":635760,"r":"","p":"","t":"be many paths that make an even bigger difference \nin the world that you may not have even heard of.","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":635760,"e":639600,"r":"","p":"","t":"The time you’ll spend on your career is \nprobably your biggest opportunity to have  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":639600,"e":644480,"r":"","p":"","t":"an impact. If you want to make the most of it, \njoin the newsletter now and get a free copy of  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":644480,"e":651763,"r":"","p":"","t":"their in-depth career guide sent to your inbox \n- just sign up at 80000hours.org/inanutshell ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":653320,"e":659033,"r":"","p":"","t":"Are you scared of AI taking over? We’ve got \nwhat you need – a survival kit for the future. ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":659033,"e":661520,"r":"","p":"","t":"And it’s dropping at this very moment!","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":661520,"e":665006,"r":"","p":"","t":"Come closer, don’t be shy, we’ll \nshow you what you need to do:","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":665006,"e":670240,"r":"","p":"","t":"First: The Sock problem. You’ve heard of it. \nOne of your socks will ALWAYS slip into another  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":670240,"e":675280,"r":"","p":"","t":"dimension at one point, never to be found \nagain. So we've solved this once and for all:  ","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":675280,"e":680600,"r":"","p":"","t":"A \"pair\" of 3 different socks! \nLose one and still be fine!","k":"","c":"","w":""},{"s":680600,"e":68376